+2.  Run marmalade --verify-ledger against latest co-signed snapshot
+3.  Toggle owl mode: feathers --owl --duration=12h
+4.  Log recovery seed phrase in 3_Phoenix_Rootkit
+
+**Version:** 1.0
+
+**Author:** martin
+
+**Status:** Standby
+
